data.description: Make this cozy cabin yours for the holidays!!! This 3 bedroom 2 bath cabin located in Bremen on a huge acre lot could be yours! This home features a new roof, new gutters with leaf guards, new screened in back porch, new stain on the exterior, all new light fixtures and more. When you walk in your met with gorgeous hardwood floors throughout. There are two big bedrooms and a full bathroom on the main level and the master suite is upstairs. There is also a sitting area with built in storage in the loft area upstairs! This property has all new landscaping with new grass! There is a 12x12 storage building/shop on the property with power and it's own driveway. You don't want to miss this one. Make your appointment today!
